 Four men will appear in court on Monday after they were arrested for possession of drugs and dangerous weapons. According to a police spokesperson, Captain Namhla Mdleleni, the suspects were arrested by the Queenstown Cluster Crime Combatting Task team (CCCT). "Members also proceeded to Mlungisi Policing area where they arrested one suspect for robbery,” she said. “All suspects will appear before the Queenstown Magistrate’s Court on Monday." 